data.description: Enjoy a comfy home on a large corner fenced lot which is nestled in a quiet & quaint neighborhood.  This home affords comfortable living space with the ability to entertain a large groups.  Enjoy a serene backyard which features a large porch, 10x20 composite wood deck area with a built in bar style serving area shaded by a large Avocado tree.  The interior of the home features family/living room, welcoming foyer area, and a large dining room.  Highly efficient 3 Ton '16 Seer AC unit' which is only 3 yrs old, S-Tile Roof installed 2003, newer appliances: stackable washer/dryer, electric self cleaning oven/stove, refrigerator & tankless water heater. The home has an alarm system, hurricane impact windows, 10x20 detached storage shed & updated main electric panel, tenting completed 12/2023. Attached:  Survey
